      "title": "Lubricant sample testing today",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The sample obtained from the amount of lubricant oil that arrived in the country will be tested today.",
        "A ship containing one lakh metric tonnes of lubricant oil has arrived in the country.",
        "It is worth noting that Power Minister Kanjana Wijesekara has said that the landing work will be carried out after its samples are tested. (a)"
      ],
